WEBVTT

00:00:00.619 --> 00:00:01.558
OUI, OUI.

00:00:01.564 --> 00:00:05.830
OUI, EN EFFET, ALORS QUAND NOUS ETIONS LA BAS, ENFERME DANS LA CHAMBRE

00:00:05.830 --> 00:00:09.710
LES TROIS GRAND, CHACUN DISAIT "OH LA LA, QU'EST-CE QUI UNK PASSE

00:00:09.710 --> 00:00:12.490
A NOTRE AGE, UN BEBE, ET CETERA, BON

00:00:12.490 --> 00:00:17.230
MAIS C'EST PAS UN TRAIN NORMAL. C'EST, C'EST ARRIVE, C'EST ARRIVE, ET VOILA

00:00:17.230 --> 00:00:19.750
QUE MAMAN ACCOUCHET UNE PETITE FILLE

00:00:19.750 --> 00:00:25.390
RENEE, ET C'EST Rokhl EN YIDDISH. C'ETAIT LE NOM DE LA MERE DE MA MERE.

00:00:25.405 --> 00:00:26.583
MA GRANDMERE

00:00:26.792 --> 00:00:29.081
QUE JE N'AI PAS CONNU, HELAS.

00:00:29.695 --> 00:00:33.455
ET ELLE EST ARRIVEE, ET MA MERE, ELLE

00:00:33.455 --> 00:00:37.252
C'ETAIT UN PETIT BEBE, ELLE AVAIT DEUX KILOS

00:00:37.252 --> 00:00:39.597
EH SIX CENT, QUELQUE CHOSE COMME CA

00:00:39.597 --> 00:00:43.065
ET EL DEVAIT S'OCCUPPER UNK SPECIALEMENT

00:00:43.065 --> 00:00:45.790
PAR CE QUE ELLE ETAIT UN PETIT

00:00:45.790 --> 00:00:47.908
UN, UN ENFANT TRES CHETIF.

00:00:47.908 --> 00:00:48.515
AH

00:00:48.515 --> 00:00:52.014
JE RE- geredt in frantseyzish. PARDON. yetst ikh kum tsurik.

00:00:51.514 --> 00:00:54.440
yo, yo, PARDON. UNK

00:00:52.122 --> 00:00:53.275
yo.

00:00:53.275 --> 00:00:54.582
neyn, neyn, neyn.

00:00:54.582 --> 00:01:00.030
ikh ken ⟨aykh⟩ zogn az di BABY iz geboyrn, un s'iz gevezn zeyer a kleyne BABY

00:01:00.030 --> 00:01:02.670
zeyer shmol, un di mame hot zikh gemuzt

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:04.720
ibergebn COMPLETE

00:01:04.760 --> 00:01:07.010
un zi hot mer nisht gekent geyn

00:01:07.010 --> 00:01:09.480
in di MAKOLET tsu helfn mayn tate.

00:01:09.638 --> 00:01:10.864
hot men gezogt

00:01:11.022 --> 00:01:14.815
ikh bin do di groyse, vayl mayn shvester iz shoyn geganen g-

00:01:14.815 --> 00:01:16.483
in di arbet

00:01:16.523 --> 00:01:22.339
un zi hot shoyn gebrengt gelt. m'hot, yeder eyner hot gemuzt brengen gelt, vayl s'hot gefelt

00:01:22.378 --> 00:01:25.716
un ikh muz geyn helfn, vayl di mame blaybt

00:01:25.716 --> 00:01:29.007
in shtub. ikh bin shoyn gevezn in UNK

00:01:29.007 --> 00:01:31.232
epes aza

00:01:31.525 --> 00:01:36.325
ikh hob mikh oyfge- adurkhgeganen di ershte BCHINOT, un ikh hob gebroykht tsu geyn vayter

00:01:36.325 --> 00:01:38.575
ober es geyt nisht mer, es geyt nisht mer.

00:01:38.575 --> 00:01:40.015
kh'hob gegat

00:01:40.015 --> 00:01:41.360
fertsn yor.

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:42.692
dos iz es.

00:01:42.692 --> 00:01:46.807
di gantse shule vos ikh hob gemakht, s'iz gevezn biz fertsn yor.

00:01:47.353 --> 00:01:50.936
iz ikh bin geganen in di MAKOLET

00:01:50.936 --> 00:01:55.294
un di tate hot geflegt tsu geyn bald in di fri, dray fir far togs

00:01:55.294 --> 00:01:57.524
in di HALLE oyf ayntsukoyfn.

00:01:57.524 --> 00:01:59.534
emetser hot gebroykht oyftsumakhn.

00:01:59.534 --> 00:02:00.900
ikh hob oyfgemakht

00:02:00.900 --> 00:02:03.668
un ikh bin dort gevezn mit di tate

00:02:03.668 --> 00:02:05.555
un s'hot gedoyert

00:02:06.017 --> 00:02:11.734
efsher nisht keyn gantse yor, biz di kleyne iz gevorn a bisele mer

00:02:11.734 --> 00:02:13.240
shtarker

00:02:13.240 --> 00:02:17.980
un damolst di mame iz, ober ikh hob shoyn mer nisht gekent tsurikgeyn

00:02:17.980 --> 00:02:19.070
in di shule

00:02:19.070 --> 00:02:22.340
un m'hot mir gelozt lernen a fakh.

00:02:22.340 --> 00:02:24.321
di fakh iz gevezn

00:02:24.321 --> 00:02:27.661
ts- mayn shvester hot in dem gearbet, in di

00:02:27.661 --> 00:02:29.470
futer.

00:02:29.470 --> 00:02:31.644
dos iz gevezn ASTRAKAN

00:02:31.903 --> 00:02:36.310
kleyne, kleyne kh- krolikes, un

00:02:36.310 --> 00:02:40.290
dos hot zey gemakht mit a mashin, un zi hot tsuzamengenumen

00:02:40.290 --> 00:02:41.780
azoy vi a PUZZLE

00:02:41.780 --> 00:02:44.122
un zi iz gevezn zeyer a shnele

00:02:44.122 --> 00:02:48.462
un damolst hot men zeyer shtark dos gebroykht. m'hot gefreyt fun iberal

00:02:48.462 --> 00:02:51.972
vayl s'iz gevezn nokh di krig, yeder eyner hot gebroykht ales

00:02:51.972 --> 00:02:53.514
vayl s'iz gornisht gevezn.

00:02:53.841 --> 00:02:57.584
un zi hot zeyer sheyn fardint, un m'hot gezogt "BERTHE oykhet"

00:02:57.584 --> 00:03:00.276
ober ikh bin nisht gevezn aza shneler

00:03:00.276 --> 00:03:04.587
un ikh bin nisht gevezn azoy gelungen in di zakhn

00:03:04.587 --> 00:03:07.099
ober m'hot gezogt, hot men gezogt.

00:03:07.307 --> 00:03:12.063
iz bin ikh geganen mikh dos oyslernen in a spetsyele shule

00:03:12.063 --> 00:03:16.042
un dernokhn bin ikh geganen arbetn in dem oykhet.

00:03:16.150 --> 00:03:23.504
un dort iz gevezn a mentsh, ober dos iz nisht, dos iz nisht azoy CHASHUV.

00:03:23.504 --> 00:03:25.897
di zakh iz az in shtub

00:03:26.376 --> 00:03:31.300
iz, s'iz gevezn a BABY. undz, undz ze'mir geganen in an andere shtub, un

00:03:31.300 --> 00:03:32.912
PITOM s'hot zikh gemakht

00:03:32.912 --> 00:03:38.084
az a mishpokhe fun undz iz aroysgeganen fun di shtub

00:03:38.084 --> 00:03:42.488
un undz ken men dort arayngeyn. s'iz shoyn gevezn a groyse shtub

00:03:42.488 --> 00:03:46.690
mit SHIRUTIM in shtub, mit a kekh, mit varem vaser.

00:03:46.690 --> 00:03:50.690
WOW, dos iz gevezn di luksus.

00:03:50.743 --> 00:03:55.811
un di BABY iz shoyn gevezn BABY, un undz ze'mir shoyn geganen dort

00:03:55.811 --> 00:04:00.924
tsu opshvenken di, damolst hot men nisht gehat di PAMPERS mit di ale zakhn.

00:04:00.924 --> 00:04:03.557
dos iz gevezn di ekhte fun shtof.

00:04:03.557 --> 00:04:06.647
dos hot men gemuzt vashn, kokhn, ahin aher

00:04:06.647 --> 00:04:10.007
un mayn shvester mit mir iz men ale mol bay nakht dort geganen

00:04:10.007 --> 00:04:11.927
oyf dos erleydikn.

00:04:11.927 --> 00:04:13.970
biz m'iz aribergeganen

00:04:13.970 --> 00:04:17.040
iz di yinglekh hobn gegat far zikh a tsimer

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:19.840
di meydlekh far zikh, di eltern far zikh

00:04:19.840 --> 00:04:21.310
un a tsimerl

00:04:21.310 --> 00:04:23.663
in di mit. dos iz gevezn

00:04:23.663 --> 00:04:28.498
m'iz gevezn azoy gliklekh, un dort iz es gevezn RUE EUGENE SUE

00:04:28.498 --> 00:04:29.569
fertsn

00:04:29.569 --> 00:04:30.764
QUATORZE

00:04:30.872 --> 00:04:35.695
oyf di tsveyte shtok. m'hot gebroykht tsu, adurkhtsugeyn ⟨HACHATSER⟩

00:04:35.695 --> 00:04:37.920
un dort iz es gevezn.

00:04:37.943 --> 00:04:40.268
dort hot men shoyn gegat shkheynim

00:04:40.268 --> 00:04:41.818
yidishe shkheynim

00:04:41.818 --> 00:04:45.128
vos oyf di ershte shtok iz gevezn eyner

00:04:45.128 --> 00:04:48.748
un oyf di drite shtok. undz ze'mir gevezn oyf di tsveyte.

00:04:48.748 --> 00:04:51.279
azoy az m'hot gegat shoyn gikher

00:04:51.279 --> 00:04:52.360
a kesher.

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:54.275
un in tsvishn s'hot zikh gemakht

00:04:54.275 --> 00:04:57.303
az di tate iz aroysgeganen fun di MAKOLET

00:04:57.303 --> 00:04:58.389
oykhet.

00:04:58.581 --> 00:05:01.190
un er hot genumen an andere MAKOLET

00:05:01.416 --> 00:05:02.771
un

00:05:02.771 --> 00:05:06.607
s'iz gevezn a sakh tayerer oyf dort arayntsugeyn

00:05:06.833 --> 00:05:08.568
un di mame

00:05:08.568 --> 00:05:13.079
mit dem alemen vos, vos s'iz nisht gevezn tsu fil fun alem

00:05:13.079 --> 00:05:14.859
zi hot nor geshport

00:05:14.859 --> 00:05:15.736
gelt

00:05:15.878 --> 00:05:20.102
un az s'iz gekumen di moment az m'hot gezogt "me darf nemen"

00:05:20.102 --> 00:05:24.664
hot zi gezogt far di tate "ikh hob do gelt in di zayt."

00:05:25.227 --> 00:05:28.106
a halbe oder dray fertl fun di skhum.

00:05:28.686 --> 00:05:32.561
un di tate iz gevezn ⟨azoy⟩ "vi azoy hostu dos gemakht?"

00:05:32.854 --> 00:05:34.991
dos iz gevezn di koyekh

00:05:35.098 --> 00:05:38.430
fun di mame vos mit gornisht

00:05:38.430 --> 00:05:41.200
hot zi nokh gemakht fun dem gornisht epes.

00:05:42.017 --> 00:05:49.920
un iz men arayngegangen in di andere, in di andere MAKOLET vos iz shoyn gevezn. dort hot men shoyn gegat gikher

00:05:49.920 --> 00:05:54.200
di koshere zakhn, un s'iz gekumen mentshn oyf peysekh

00:05:54.200 --> 00:05:57.610
un peysekh ale kinder, zey hobn dort geholfn

00:05:57.610 --> 00:06:01.410
mit di matses, un mit dos un mit yents un mit di vareme

00:06:01.744 --> 00:06:04.850
s'hot zikh gemakht shoyn a sakh beser, di gantse

00:06:04.850 --> 00:06:07.100
di gantse MATSAV, un

00:06:07.100 --> 00:06:10.760
un dort iz men shoyn gevezn ruik

00:06:10.772 --> 00:06:13.111
un di

00:06:13.624 --> 00:06:17.178
ober BECHOL ZOT hot men gevart oyf di shvester.

00:06:17.708 --> 00:06:19.980
ale mol hot men geklert

00:06:21.184 --> 00:06:22.151
efsher

00:06:22.151 --> 00:06:26.206
efsher. di mame hot gezogt "efsher me hot zi genumen in Rusland.

00:06:26.331 --> 00:06:29.852
efsher zi iz bahaltn in a plats vos me veyst nisht."

00:06:30.111 --> 00:06:32.872
ale mol iz gevezn di gedank

00:06:33.435 --> 00:06:34.933
BECHOL ZOT

00:06:34.933 --> 00:06:39.017
az zi vet kumen, un in tsvishn ikh bin gevorn a groys

00:06:39.017 --> 00:06:39.976
meydl

00:06:40.101 --> 00:06:41.124
un

00:06:41.468 --> 00:06:46.780
di ershte mol vos ikh hob, vos ikh bin geforn keyn Yisroel

00:06:46.780 --> 00:06:48.290
mit a khaverte.

00:06:48.290 --> 00:06:51.252
m'iz geforn mit a shif durkh

00:06:51.252 --> 00:06:55.336
NAPOLI mit, fun MARSEILLE a gantse

00:06:55.336 --> 00:06:57.893
mit a tsug, mit ahin aher

00:06:57.893 --> 00:07:02.643
un mayn tate fun di MAKOLET. m'hot gevust in Yisroel iz gornisht do damolst.

00:07:02.643 --> 00:07:04.660
s'iz gevezn efsher in

00:07:04.660 --> 00:07:06.133
finef un fuftsik

00:07:06.460 --> 00:07:09.441
epes aza zakh. s'iz gevezn ⟨detsember⟩

00:07:09.447 --> 00:07:13.587
hot men genumen a groyse vursht mit ale sardinen

00:07:13.587 --> 00:07:16.387
mit ale zakhn, mit pushkes

00:07:16.387 --> 00:07:18.277
ales, a groyse CARTON

00:07:18.277 --> 00:07:20.184
PLUS ikh hob gegat mayn valizke

00:07:20.184 --> 00:07:22.547
s'iz gevezn a groyse zakh tsu shlepn.

00:07:22.547 --> 00:07:27.370
un m'hot gebrengt fun do biz dort un dort un hin, ahin, ahin aher

00:07:27.400 --> 00:07:29.828
ober m'hot zikh gegebn an eytse

00:07:29.828 --> 00:07:33.465
un m'hot, m'iz gevezn yung. s'iz nisht gevezn keyn BAAYA

00:07:33.465 --> 00:07:35.996
un ikh bin gekumen in Yisroel

00:07:35.996 --> 00:07:37.436
bay mayn mume.

00:07:37.982 --> 00:07:39.346
di mume iz UNK

00:07:39.346 --> 00:07:41.539
Dvoyre olevasholem.

00:07:41.539 --> 00:07:43.291
zi hot mir oyfgenumen

00:07:43.635 --> 00:07:45.552
azoy vi a printses

00:07:45.643 --> 00:07:51.357
un zi heybt mir on tsu fregn "un dayn mame," zi hot zi nisht gegat gezen fertsik yor.

00:07:51.516 --> 00:07:53.430
a, a, a velt

00:07:53.430 --> 00:07:55.113
un fun Poyln

00:07:55.113 --> 00:07:58.383
vos zi iz geforn keyn Yisroel, un zi iz geforn keyn Pariz.

00:07:58.550 --> 00:08:02.760
ikh hob gevolt dertseyln, un mayn yidish iz gevezn azoy

00:08:02.760 --> 00:08:05.450
nebekhdik

00:08:05.470 --> 00:08:08.980
az s'iz gevezn a shrek. kh'hob mikh gevolt klapn.

00:08:09.070 --> 00:08:12.340
far vos ken ikh nisht beser keyn yidish

00:08:12.370 --> 00:08:14.470
oyf tsu kenen redn mit ir?

00:08:14.584 --> 00:08:18.724
un mit di hent un mit di fis. ober di libe iz gevezn groys.

00:08:18.724 --> 00:08:21.480
un mayn feter un mayn mume

00:08:21.638 --> 00:08:25.715
kh'bin gekumen far eyn monat. ikh bin geblibn zeks.

00:08:26.127 --> 00:08:28.365
di mame hot gegat geshribn a briv

00:08:28.371 --> 00:08:30.677
"zukh a shidekh far mayn tokhter."

00:08:31.273 --> 00:08:34.046
dos iz gevezn di gantse zakh.

00:08:34.046 --> 00:08:38.640
un ikh bin gevezn azoy gut, hob ikh mir getrakht "vos darf ikh aheymgeyn in Pariz?

00:08:38.640 --> 00:08:42.390
ikh hob do a BADE tsimer in Yisroel, hob ikh di groyse luksus.

00:08:42.390 --> 00:08:46.450
un ven s'hot mir gefelt epes gelt, ikh bin geganen bay di feter.

00:08:46.450 --> 00:08:49.240
kh'hob im gezogt "du veyst? ikh darf mir makhn di hor."

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:53.040
hot er gezogt "ah, vifl es kost?" shoyn gezogt "fir LIROT." "vos?

00:08:53.040 --> 00:08:55.170
mayn tokhter, zi makht far tsvey LIROT."

00:08:55.199 --> 00:08:57.550
"yo, ober iz, ikh bin a BACHURA.

00:08:57.550 --> 00:08:59.320
du vilst makhn mit mir a shidekh.

00:08:59.320 --> 00:09:03.440
ikh darf hobn sheyn." ahin, un ales, hot er mir nokhgegebn

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:05.380
un s'iz gekumen vinter

00:09:05.380 --> 00:09:06.400
a bisl

00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:09.290
un ikh bin gekumen mit zumerdike zakhn

00:09:09.880 --> 00:09:16.190
iz vos tut men? ikh hob ober gesh- gezogt, a briv, "shik mir di zakhn fun vinter."

00:09:16.190 --> 00:09:21.530
di vinter. ober dervayl muz men epes hobn. zi iz geganen mit mir, un zi hot mir gekoyft a kleyd

00:09:21.532 --> 00:09:25.675
ahin aher, un s'iz ir gut geganen, BARUCH HASHEM, ober

00:09:25.675 --> 00:09:27.918
s'iz gevezn mitn gantsn ⟨harts⟩.

00:09:27.918 --> 00:09:30.818
un do hob ikh ongehoybn tsu geyn mit shidukhim

00:09:31.669 --> 00:09:38.196
un ikh hob gezen farshidene ⟨tipes⟩ vos ikh bin nisht gevezn tsugevoynt mit dem, ah, fun do, fun dort

00:09:38.196 --> 00:09:41.546
yeder, m'hot gezukht emetsn vos zol redn yidish

00:09:41.546 --> 00:09:44.176
vayl keyn IVRIT hob ikh zikher nisht gekent.

00:09:44.176 --> 00:09:45.196
un

00:09:45.253 --> 00:09:49.440
ikh veys nisht fun vu, on a tam, on a reyekh, s'iz a

00:09:49.471 --> 00:09:55.921
dort bin ikh a Parizer meydl, un do, ikh hob nisht gevust vi azoy me heyst dos.

00:09:55.921 --> 00:09:58.121
biz s'iz gekumen

00:09:58.121 --> 00:09:59.591
der rikhtiker.

00:09:59.648 --> 00:10:03.827
un dos iz gevezn a belgisher, un s'iz gevezn

00:10:03.968 --> 00:10:07.472
m'hot mir forgeshtelt

00:10:07.647 --> 00:10:08.630
un

00:10:08.630 --> 00:10:10.914
m'iz gevorn khosn kale.

00:10:10.760 --> 00:10:13.120
vos iz gevezn zayn nomen?

00:10:12.085 --> 00:10:14.550
zayn nomen iz gevezn KOENIG

00:10:14.550 --> 00:10:16.250
un er hot geheysn Berl.

00:10:16.250 --> 00:10:18.874
Berl KOENIG. un ikh hob yetst

00:10:18.874 --> 00:10:21.714
a sakh eyniklekh vos heysn Berl

00:10:21.838 --> 00:10:23.232
oyf zayn nomen.

00:10:23.408 --> 00:10:26.389
un m'iz tsurikgekumen khosn kale.

00:10:26.952 --> 00:10:30.641
mayn shvester hot undz gevart bay di, bay di

00:10:30.968 --> 00:10:31.901
tsug.

00:10:31.901 --> 00:10:36.665
keyner hot nisht gekent azoy gut, ober er hot yo geredt frantseyzish

00:10:36.773 --> 00:10:39.740
vayl BEMIKRE er iz gevezn ⟨in⟩ Antverpn.

00:10:39.740 --> 00:10:41.923
s'hot im zeyer gefeln di shprakh

00:10:41.923 --> 00:10:45.563
hot er zikh genumen private SHIURUM, un er hot gekent

00:10:45.563 --> 00:10:48.073
herlekh shraybn un redn.

00:10:49.108 --> 00:10:51.560
mit an aktsent, avade, ober

00:10:51.560 --> 00:10:52.725
er hot gekent.

00:10:52.725 --> 00:10:55.930
un azoy hot men zikh, m'iz gekumen khosn kale.

00:10:55.930 --> 00:10:59.570
di mame hot zikh zeyer gefreyt, a yidisher yungerman

00:10:59.570 --> 00:11:02.715
a frumer, vos ken men beser veln?

00:11:02.715 --> 00:11:08.610
⟨in dem⟩ Pariz, vos iz nisht gevezn azoy, m'hot es nisht getrofn azoy laykht

00:11:08.610 --> 00:11:09.521
un

00:11:09.544 --> 00:11:13.759
ikh bin gevorn a kale. ikh bin gekumen keyn Antverpn

00:11:13.759 --> 00:11:16.675
oyf bazukh, koydem kol bay zayn mishpokhe

00:11:17.509 --> 00:11:18.552
un

00:11:20.361 --> 00:11:24.607
ikh bin gekumen nokh di khasene. ikh hob khasene gegat in Pariz

00:11:24.816 --> 00:11:29.588
in a plats vos heyst SABRINA. s'iz gevezn a kleyne

00:11:29.588 --> 00:11:31.678
a kleyne zal.

00:11:32.376 --> 00:11:37.162
nisht gevezn azoy fil keyn koshere pletser azoy vi s'iz do hayn- haynt

00:11:37.202 --> 00:11:40.723
ober m'iz gevezn nisht tsu fil mentshn oykhet

00:11:40.915 --> 00:11:41.854
un

00:11:41.961 --> 00:11:45.999
kh'hob dort khasene. m'iz geblibn a por tog, un m'iz glaykh geganen

00:11:45.999 --> 00:11:47.591
voynen in Antverpn.

00:11:48.272 --> 00:11:51.732
un in Antverpn iz gevezn an andere velt.

00:11:51.732 --> 00:11:53.982
yidn hobn geredt frantseyzish

00:11:54.465 --> 00:11:58.036
ober s'iz nisht gevezn di zelbe gedanken.

00:11:58.127 --> 00:12:01.080
ikh hob gezogt "me redt di zelbe shprakh

00:12:01.080 --> 00:12:03.030
ober me farshteyt zikh nisht."

00:12:03.030 --> 00:12:05.529
s'iz KEILU s'iz do a vant.

00:12:05.974 --> 00:12:08.139
a durkhzikhtike vant

00:12:08.139 --> 00:12:09.447
vos me ken nisht

00:12:09.447 --> 00:12:10.862
komunikirn.

00:12:11.813 --> 00:12:13.902
es iz mir gevezn zeyer shver.

00:12:13.902 --> 00:12:16.509
kh'bin geblibn biz ikh hob gegat

00:12:16.509 --> 00:12:19.232
a yor mit a halb shpeter mayn tokhter

00:12:19.828 --> 00:12:23.040
bin ikh, kh'hob nisht gevolt aroysgeyn. kh- kh-

00:12:23.040 --> 00:12:26.852
vos ikh bin ale mol gevezn a lebediker mentsh un ales

00:12:26.852 --> 00:12:29.492
un dort bin ikh farfaln gevorn.

00:12:29.548 --> 00:12:32.388
kh'hob nisht gekent, kh'hob nisht gevust vos un ven

00:12:32.388 --> 00:12:35.499
iz ikh bin adurkhgeganen a shvere TKUFA

00:12:36.012 --> 00:12:37.791
biz kh'hob gegat mayn BABY.

00:12:37.791 --> 00:12:40.801
az ven ikh hob gegat mayn BABY bin ikh tsurik gevorn

00:12:40.801 --> 00:12:43.891
a mentsh, aroysgeganen, getrofn andere mames

00:12:43.891 --> 00:12:45.490
mit andere BABIES

00:12:45.490 --> 00:12:47.210
un s'hot zikh shoyn gemakht

00:12:47.210 --> 00:12:48.864
a bisl mer

00:12:48.864 --> 00:12:54.224
mer heymlekh., ikh hob getrofn eyne fun LONDON un eyner fun BRUXELLES

00:12:54.224 --> 00:12:56.144
nisht, un eyne fun TANGIERS

00:12:56.144 --> 00:12:59.004
nisht spetsyel keyn geboyrene Antverpener

00:12:59.004 --> 00:13:02.769
vayl s'iz gevezn an andere UNK bikhlal.

00:13:02.893 --> 00:13:07.362
un es hot zikh gemakht LEAT LEAT. m'hot, m'hot, m'hot zikh ayngelebt

00:13:07.362 --> 00:13:10.045
un dernokhn hob ikh gegat mayn tsveyte BABY

00:13:10.045 --> 00:13:13.226
un dernokhn hob ikh gehat di drite

00:13:13.226 --> 00:13:17.369
un di ferde, di, di yingste

00:13:17.369 --> 00:13:19.090
un nisht

00:13:19.090 --> 00:13:21.180
nisht lang nokh dem

00:13:22.418 --> 00:13:24.622
s'iz geshen di umglik.

00:13:24.932 --> 00:13:26.664
di tate iz avek.

00:13:27.193 --> 00:13:28.317
mayn man.

00:13:29.320 --> 00:13:31.153
er iz nifter gevorn.

00:13:31.277 --> 00:13:33.144
er iz nifter gevorn

00:13:33.370 --> 00:13:36.818
ven er hot gebrengt zayn zun in di yeshive

00:13:36.818 --> 00:13:38.089
in Yisroel.

00:13:38.449 --> 00:13:41.230
er hot shoyn gegat fuftsn un a halb yor.

00:13:41.230 --> 00:13:44.146
er hot gezogt "s'iz nishto vu im tsu shikn"

00:13:44.760 --> 00:13:47.204
un dos, azoy iz gevezn MEKUBAL.

00:13:47.204 --> 00:13:49.193
me geyt im shikn in Yisroel.

00:13:49.215 --> 00:13:55.042
er hot shoyn gegat farshidene problem mitn harts mit ales. haynt iz dos gornisht

00:13:55.042 --> 00:13:57.321
ober damolst iz es yo gevezn

00:13:57.321 --> 00:14:01.376
epes. vi vayt er iz geganen bay groyse profesorn, ahin aher

00:14:01.821 --> 00:14:04.341
ober dos iz es, un

00:14:04.341 --> 00:14:06.557
er hot im gebrengt in Yisroel

00:14:06.580 --> 00:14:07.384
un

00:14:07.845 --> 00:14:09.948
s'iz, er iz do geblibn.

00:14:10.765 --> 00:14:14.195
un mir hot men prubirt tsu klingen in a shabes.

00:14:14.195 --> 00:14:16.428
s'iz gevezn in mitn shabes.

00:14:16.452 --> 00:14:19.039
un dem klung vos m'hot ale mol

00:14:19.039 --> 00:14:21.696
di harts hot mir shoyn gekhalesht

00:14:21.696 --> 00:14:24.646
vos nokh un nokh un nokh di klung

00:14:24.889 --> 00:14:28.362
vet nisht ⟨oyf biz⟩, kh'hob gezogt s'iz nisht normal.

00:14:28.362 --> 00:14:31.340
ikh gey klingen. un do klingt mir a kuzine

00:14:31.340 --> 00:14:35.379
"BERTHE, kum shnel, anisht vestu nisht hobn far vos tsu kumen."

00:14:36.027 --> 00:14:38.782
ober dervayl di umglik iz shoyn gevezn.

00:14:38.782 --> 00:14:40.627
kh'bin nisht gekumen bay tsaytns

00:14:40.971 --> 00:14:42.180
leyder.

00:14:43.148 --> 00:14:49.470
un, un ikh, ikh hob getrakht "OKAY, me darf yetst geyn."

00:14:49.470 --> 00:14:52.360
kh'hob nisht gegat keyn gelt, keyn dos. ikh bin shnel geganen

00:14:52.360 --> 00:14:54.520
bay a shokhnte, un ikh bin gevezn damolst

00:14:54.520 --> 00:14:55.460
in HEIDE

00:14:55.460 --> 00:14:57.655
in, in droysn fun di shtot

00:14:57.728 --> 00:14:59.460
vayl s'iz gevezn zumer.

00:15:00.040 --> 00:15:05.046
un mayn tokhter, di o- di groyse, hot mir gezogt "ikh for mit dir"

00:15:05.203 --> 00:15:06.395
vayl

00:15:06.891 --> 00:15:12.752
un m'iz geganen. m'hot gekoyft oyfn plats a KARTIS, un m'hot gebroykht tsu makhn a STOP in ZURICH

00:15:12.752 --> 00:15:15.382
un m'hot nisht gekent tsurikforn, ahin aher.

00:15:15.382 --> 00:15:17.402
s'hot zikh gemakht a gantse BILBUL

00:15:17.402 --> 00:15:20.272
un ikh hob nisht gevust vu ikh bin bikhlal.

00:15:20.272 --> 00:15:22.582
nor gut az zi iz gevezn lebn mir

00:15:22.582 --> 00:15:24.218
vayl s'iz mir

00:15:24.218 --> 00:15:28.181
KEILU di erd hot zikh oyfgemakht.

00:15:28.525 --> 00:15:30.054
s'iz gevezn

00:15:30.128 --> 00:15:32.951
a geferlekhe zakh. ikh bin gekumen

00:15:32.951 --> 00:15:34.360
oyf di levaye

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:35.471
leyder.

00:15:36.220 --> 00:15:39.980
un di yingl hot oykhet gegat a groyse CHOC

00:15:39.980 --> 00:15:41.006
fun dem

00:15:41.130 --> 00:15:42.131
avade.

00:15:42.131 --> 00:15:44.426
iz azoy iz men geblibn.

00:15:44.426 --> 00:15:47.927
kh'hob gegat a tokhter vos zi hot nokh nisht gegat zibetsn yor

00:15:47.927 --> 00:15:51.232
di bokher fun finef m- fuftsn mit a halbe

00:15:51.255 --> 00:15:54.624
mit a yingele fun nayn mit a halbe

00:15:54.917 --> 00:15:58.623
un di meydele vos hot nisht gegat keyn dray yor.

00:15:59.423 --> 00:16:01.408
kleyne kinder BEETSEM.

00:16:02.832 --> 00:16:05.981
s'hot zikh ongehoybn a shvere

00:16:06.173 --> 00:16:07.247
TKUFA.

00:16:07.472 --> 00:16:08.512
zeyer.

00:16:10.645 --> 00:16:16.541
di, s'iz gevezn in di ale shlekhte zakhn iz ale mol do a gute zayt az

00:16:16.541 --> 00:16:18.481
ikh bin gevezn bavornt.

00:16:18.481 --> 00:16:19.577
BARUCH HASHEM.

00:16:19.577 --> 00:16:22.175
kh'hob nisht gebroykht tsu geyn arbetn mit ales

00:16:22.175 --> 00:16:23.652
er hot mir gelozt

00:16:23.652 --> 00:16:25.500
far mayne kinder un far mir

00:16:25.500 --> 00:16:27.331
vos me darf oyf tsu kenen

00:16:27.331 --> 00:16:28.256
lebn.

00:16:28.498 --> 00:16:31.930
un di kinder zenen geganen vayter. di meydl

00:16:31.930 --> 00:16:33.590
ahin aher

00:16:33.590 --> 00:16:34.668
un

00:16:35.856 --> 00:16:37.684
ikh hob

00:16:37.684 --> 00:16:39.920
kh'hob mir shver getrofn

00:16:39.920 --> 00:16:42.485
vayl in Antverpn iz a kleyne shtot.

00:16:42.485 --> 00:16:44.099
un yeder eyner

00:16:44.099 --> 00:16:45.939
ven ikh bin adurkhgeganen

00:16:45.939 --> 00:16:48.959
s'iz azoy vi di gantse historye geyt mir nokh

00:16:48.959 --> 00:16:52.529
m'hot ongehoybn tsu zogn "ah zi

00:16:52.530 --> 00:16:55.590
zi iz aleyn, zi iz a almone, zi iz dos un yents"

00:16:55.590 --> 00:16:59.191
un s'iz nokh gevezn shverer. anshtat az me zol

00:16:59.191 --> 00:17:00.014
neyn.

00:17:01.118 --> 00:17:02.715
hob ikh bashlosn

00:17:03.075 --> 00:17:04.790
ikh for keyn Yisroel.

00:17:05.656 --> 00:17:09.970
un yeder eyner hot mir gezogt, kh'hob dokh gegat zeyer a groyse gezelshaft

00:17:10.196 --> 00:17:15.018
mit mentsh, yeder eyner ken zikh. "vos geystu dort makhn?"

00:17:15.018 --> 00:17:16.328
mayne shvegerin.

00:17:16.328 --> 00:17:19.306
"bist eyne aleyn. host dort nisht keyn mishpokhe.

00:17:19.306 --> 00:17:21.854
host nokh nisht, du kenst nisht di shprakh.

00:17:21.854 --> 00:17:23.580
m'vet dikh onfaln.

00:17:23.580 --> 00:17:27.750
m'vet zen a froy, un dos un yents, m'vet dikh baganvenen," ah?

00:17:27.750 --> 00:17:29.985
vos hot men mir nisht gezogt?

00:17:30.278 --> 00:17:32.077
vu geystu?

00:17:32.252 --> 00:17:36.819
ober ikh bin gevezn als a yung kind in BNE AKIVA.

00:17:37.365 --> 00:17:40.754
un in BNE AKIVA hob ikh gegat, hob, hot men mir gut

00:17:40.754 --> 00:17:42.205
arayngeflantst

00:17:42.205 --> 00:17:44.973
un di libe far Yisroel iz gevezn shtark.

00:17:44.973 --> 00:17:46.640
shtarker vi ales.

00:17:47.085 --> 00:17:48.423
un ikh hob gezogt

00:17:48.423 --> 00:17:52.023
"mayn zun iz in di yeshive. er iz dort aleyn.

00:17:52.030 --> 00:17:54.218
ikh bin do mit di kinder

00:17:54.291 --> 00:17:58.141
un ikh muz aleyn makhn kidesh, aleyn makhn havdole.

00:17:58.141 --> 00:17:59.591
ikh muz ales makhn.

00:17:59.591 --> 00:18:01.601
kh'hob a bar mitsve bokher

00:18:01.601 --> 00:18:03.561
vos er ken mir yo epes makhn.

00:18:03.561 --> 00:18:05.391
far vos zoln mir nisht zayn tsuzamen?

00:18:05.391 --> 00:18:06.561
s'iz gevezn nisht

00:18:06.561 --> 00:18:07.601
UNK

00:18:07.601 --> 00:18:09.470
az ikh zol zikh dort mutshen

00:18:09.470 --> 00:18:11.128
un ikh do aleyn."

00:18:11.128 --> 00:18:14.149
s'hot nisht gegat keyn shum shpa- pshat.

00:18:14.149 --> 00:18:17.927
ober vos in tsvishn, mayn tokhter iz gevorn a kale

00:18:18.102 --> 00:18:19.311
di groyse

00:18:19.401 --> 00:18:22.186
vos UNK, dos iz oykhet gevezn a gantse

00:18:22.186 --> 00:18:24.496
SIPUR ⟨vayl zukhn mir⟩ nisht tsu shpreytn

00:18:24.496 --> 00:18:27.326
ober ikh bin gevezn a bisl modern

00:18:27.326 --> 00:18:28.746
fun di MIZRACHI

00:18:28.746 --> 00:18:31.736
un mayn tokhter hot gevolt a Belzer khosid

00:18:32.428 --> 00:18:34.767
un dos hot zi bakumen

00:18:35.078 --> 00:18:38.399
un ikh hob getrakht "vi azoy vel ikh dos esn?

00:18:38.399 --> 00:18:41.332
vi azoy geyt men tsu tsu aza zakh?

00:18:41.490 --> 00:18:43.259
a froy aleyn

00:18:43.259 --> 00:18:44.285
vos

00:18:44.359 --> 00:18:46.470
kh'veys nisht vi azoy."

00:18:46.470 --> 00:18:49.190
di tate iz take gevezn a Belzer khosid.

00:18:49.190 --> 00:18:50.833
a moderne, avade

00:18:51.340 --> 00:18:54.450
un ikh bin nisht gevezn gedekt

00:18:54.450 --> 00:18:57.009
un di, di hor mit alemen

00:18:57.471 --> 00:18:58.460
ober

00:18:58.534 --> 00:19:01.210
UNK kh'hob gegat a spetsyele tokhter

00:19:01.210 --> 00:19:02.720
vos di

00:19:02.720 --> 00:19:03.483
vos

00:19:03.483 --> 00:19:05.129
ir gantse

00:19:05.129 --> 00:19:11.340
groyskeyt, hot men gekent in gants Antverpn. zi hot gegebn shiurim bay do Belzer, ales ⟨HITLAHAVUT⟩

00:19:11.340 --> 00:19:14.210
un dos un yents hot gemakht a groyse ROSHEM.

00:19:14.250 --> 00:19:17.144
un di mentshn fun Amerike hobn dos gehert.

00:19:17.144 --> 00:19:18.780
m'hot gemakht dem shidekh.

00:19:18.780 --> 00:19:19.571
un

00:19:19.712 --> 00:19:23.435
zenen tsugeganen dertsu, afilet az bay di frume

00:19:23.435 --> 00:19:26.245
un di khsidishe hot men lib tsu hobn a mekhutn

00:19:26.245 --> 00:19:28.410
un do iz nisht gevezn keyn mekhutn.

00:19:28.410 --> 00:19:30.410
ikh hob gebroykht tsu zayn i di mekhutn

00:19:30.410 --> 00:19:35.530
i di mekhuteneste vos koym, ikh bin azoy vakldik

00:19:35.530 --> 00:19:37.960
un ikh veys nisht vi azoy tsu makhn.

00:19:37.960 --> 00:19:38.860
ober

00:19:39.220 --> 00:19:40.263
di koyekh

00:19:40.263 --> 00:19:42.065
di RATSON iz do.

00:19:42.207 --> 00:19:44.169
un s'iz far mayn kind.

00:19:44.169 --> 00:19:45.811
es iz nisht stam

00:19:45.919 --> 00:19:47.077
hob ikh getrakht

00:19:47.100 --> 00:19:48.764
ikh'l ales makhn.

00:19:48.923 --> 00:19:53.771
un ikh bin gevezn tsugevoynt als a meydl, hob ikh geshpilt a sakh

00:19:53.771 --> 00:19:58.991
oyf di, tsu makhn HATSAGOT, mit ales. ale mol hot men mikh genumen, vayl

00:19:59.132 --> 00:20:01.567
kh'hob es gekent, hob ikh gezogt OKAY.

00:20:01.567 --> 00:20:04.104
dos iz di HATSAGA fun di CHAIM.

00:20:04.347 --> 00:20:09.066
azoy vel ikh muzn shpiln azoy vi m'vet veln.

00:20:09.156 --> 00:20:10.955
un azoy iz gevezn.

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:16.594
un ⟨m- ikh hob ⟩ bakumen di, m'hot mir gezogt "gey zen di khosn

00:20:16.594 --> 00:20:21.480
d- di bokher." vos zol ikh zen? vos zol ikh zogn? ven? vu?

00:20:21.480 --> 00:20:23.138
ikh ze a bokher.

00:20:23.138 --> 00:20:27.288
kh'bin geblibn in gantsn ⟨oys⟩. vos vil men fun mir?

00:20:27.415 --> 00:20:33.299
OKAY. kh'hob im gek- -zen, un er zogt "ah, di shviger, ENFIN di"

00:20:33.299 --> 00:20:36.929
er hot gemakht a ROSHEM. ikh veys nisht mit vos, ikh veys nisht mit ven.

00:20:36.929 --> 00:20:42.202
⟨shir⟩ az di eybershter vil iz nishto keyn shum problem.

00:20:42.202 --> 00:20:46.379
ales iz adurkhgeganen ⟨KESHUR⟩, un me hot gemakht a sheyne khasene

00:20:46.379 --> 00:20:50.471
un s'iz, s'iz azoy. un zi iz geforn keyn Amerike

00:20:50.471 --> 00:20:51.894
bin ikh geblibn mit

00:20:51.900 --> 00:20:53.432
tsvey kleyne kinder

00:20:53.432 --> 00:20:57.041
un di groyse i- dort. iz damolst hob ikh bashlosn

00:20:57.267 --> 00:20:58.605
dos iz es.

00:20:58.605 --> 00:21:01.293
ikh g- ikh for oykhet. ikh for keyn Yisroel.

00:21:01.367 --> 00:21:06.060
kh'bin geganen in Amerike a por mol bazukhn, iz di eltern, di gantse mekhutonim

00:21:06.060 --> 00:21:08.170
"vos geyt ir makhn in Yisroel?

00:21:08.170 --> 00:21:09.870
kumts in Amerike."

00:21:09.906 --> 00:21:13.579
un mayn tokhter zogt mir "host gornisht vos tsu tun in Amerike

00:21:13.618 --> 00:21:17.327
vos di, di, ts- tsulib," neyn.

00:21:17.327 --> 00:21:20.413
un nokh gut, zi hot gevust ve- vos ikh bin

00:21:20.413 --> 00:21:22.433
vos iz mayn PERSONALITE.

00:21:22.433 --> 00:21:24.363
ikh hob gornisht azoy vayt

00:21:24.373 --> 00:21:26.761
biz haynt kh'hob es nisht lib Amerike.

00:21:26.761 --> 00:21:29.485
ikh bin ⟨zhe⟩ ikh for shoyn azoy fil mol

00:21:29.485 --> 00:21:32.945
un s'i- ikh hob nisht lib di shprakh. ikh hob nisht lib keyn english.

00:21:32.945 --> 00:21:35.305
ikh vil es nisht lernen. ZEHU ZE.

00:21:35.522 --> 00:21:39.240
efsher vayl zey hobn mir genumen mayn tokhter. ZE LO CHASHUV vos

00:21:39.240 --> 00:21:40.330
epes, ikh

00:21:40.330 --> 00:21:45.140
prubir tsu analizirn. s'ken zayn az s'iz do, LO CHASHUV.

00:21:45.140 --> 00:21:47.969
ikh hob nisht lib Amerike. NEKUDA.

00:21:48.178 --> 00:21:51.710
iz ikh gey oyf simkhes mit groyse fargenign, ober

00:21:51.710 --> 00:21:53.160
shnel ikh kum tsurik

00:21:53.195 --> 00:21:55.006
⟨vos⟩ vayt meglekh.

00:21:55.114 --> 00:21:57.460
un ikh bin gekumen in Yisroel

00:21:57.460 --> 00:21:59.650
un ikh hob mir gekoyft a dire.

00:21:59.650 --> 00:22:01.760
dos ikh gevezn oyf RECHOV HAYARDEN

00:22:01.760 --> 00:22:05.809
vayl di mentsh vos er hot gemakht di binyen iz gevezn a khaver fun mayn man.

00:22:05.809 --> 00:22:09.767
m'hot gekoyft a toplte dire, zol zayn breyt, zol zayn bakvem.

00:22:09.767 --> 00:22:13.607
mayn zun hot gebrengt di ale yeshive bokherim fun CHUTS LAARETS

00:22:13.607 --> 00:22:15.700
vos zey hobn nisht gegat vu vos ven

00:22:15.700 --> 00:22:19.470
zenen geganen rekhts. ikh mit di tokhter bin geganen links

00:22:19.470 --> 00:22:21.525
un azoy hot zikh gemakht.

00:22:21.525 --> 00:22:23.485
m'hot zikh oyfgeboyt

00:22:23.485 --> 00:22:27.735
LEAT LEAT a shtikl lebn, un azoy vi ikh hob ⟨keyner⟩ nisht gekent

00:22:27.739 --> 00:22:30.730
a por mentshn Antverpener vos zenen do gekumen

00:22:30.730 --> 00:22:33.280
bin ikh geganen nokh a mol bay di MIZRACHI.

00:22:33.280 --> 00:22:34.700
ikh hob gezogt

00:22:34.700 --> 00:22:36.120
ikh bin do.

00:22:36.120 --> 00:22:40.430
ikh hob gearbet in di MIZRACHI in Antverpn. efsher ken men epes do makhn.

00:22:40.430 --> 00:22:43.620
ikh shtel mir for. "ikh bin BERTHE KOENIG"

00:22:43.620 --> 00:22:44.690
VEZEHU ZE.

00:22:44.690 --> 00:22:49.250
"ah" zogt men. "gut, vos kenstu tun?" zog ikh "ah, ikh ken oyfnemen

00:22:49.250 --> 00:22:50.610
kh'hob a groyse shtub."

00:22:50.613 --> 00:22:51.786
"ah, gut."

00:22:51.786 --> 00:22:54.756
un azoy hot men gemakht bay mir kontsertn

00:22:54.756 --> 00:22:57.346
un HATSAGOT fun TMUNOT

00:22:57.346 --> 00:22:59.566
mit alemen, un s'iz gevorn

00:22:59.566 --> 00:23:02.566
heymlekh far di k- kh'hob gevolt far di kinder

00:23:02.566 --> 00:23:04.356
zoln nisht zayn eynzam

00:23:04.356 --> 00:23:07.846
az mentshn zoln araynkumen. s'iz nisht keyn khilek ver.

00:23:07.846 --> 00:23:09.316
⟨ZU SHEHIYE.⟩

00:23:09.316 --> 00:23:15.650
iz azoy hot zikh gemakht, un ikh hob genumen bilder, un m'hot geshikt far di tokhter, "kuk vos do tut zikh."

00:23:15.650 --> 00:23:18.830
s'iz gevezn, zi hot zikh nisht gekent gloybn.

00:23:18.830 --> 00:23:21.870
un dos, un d- azoy iz es adurkhgeganen.

00:23:21.870 --> 00:23:25.300
ikh bin geblibn, ikh bin gekumen in oygust

00:23:25.300 --> 00:23:27.160
zibn un zibetsik

00:23:27.319 --> 00:23:33.630
un do hob ikh gegat kha- gute khavertes fun Belgye vos zenen, vos zenen nokhgeganen mit mir

00:23:33.630 --> 00:23:34.710
di gantse tsayt

00:23:34.710 --> 00:23:36.720
un eyne fun di CHAVERIM

00:23:36.720 --> 00:23:38.090
hot mir forgeshtelt

00:23:38.090 --> 00:23:39.100
a shidekh

00:23:39.100 --> 00:23:41.828
un dos iz gevezn mayn man. un nokh

00:23:41.828 --> 00:23:45.068
eyn yor mit a halb vos ikh bin gevezn do in land

00:23:45.068 --> 00:23:45.760
hob ikh

00:23:45.760 --> 00:23:48.283
khasene gemakht, khasene gegat

00:23:48.283 --> 00:23:50.544
mit mayn tsveyte ziveg.

00:23:50.544 --> 00:23:52.881
un dos iz Oyzer GRUNDMAN

00:23:52.881 --> 00:23:57.131
vos, me lebt shoyn ariber di tsvantsik yor tsuzamen

00:23:57.255 --> 00:23:59.766
biz hundert un tsvantsik, un

00:23:59.766 --> 00:24:03.217
m'hot nisht gegat keyn kinder tsuzamen, ober

00:24:03.217 --> 00:24:04.932
a sakh eyniklekh yo

00:24:04.932 --> 00:24:08.352
vos me ken zogn az m'hot dos gegat tsuzamen.

00:24:08.352 --> 00:24:13.972
vayl m'iz gelof- loyfn tsuzamen ven s'iz gevezn a geburts in di shpitol un do un dort

00:24:13.972 --> 00:24:18.860
hot men shoyn dos ales, er hot zey gezen kleyn, un er hot zey getrogn

00:24:18.860 --> 00:24:22.160
azoy az s'hot undz shtark gebundn

00:24:22.160 --> 00:24:24.468
di gantse, di gantse zakh.

00:24:24.694 --> 00:24:26.510
iz

00:24:26.618 --> 00:24:29.464
mayn lebn in Yisroel iz gevezn

00:24:29.655 --> 00:24:31.876
a gut lebn, ikh ken zogn

00:24:32.085 --> 00:24:37.861
un mayn tokhter iz gekumen shpeter nokh a gevise tsayt fun Amerike

00:24:37.861 --> 00:24:40.399
un zi hot do geloybt tsen yor

00:24:40.810 --> 00:24:42.188
in Yisroel

00:24:42.582 --> 00:24:44.976
biz di tate iz gevorn krank

00:24:44.976 --> 00:24:46.906
fun mayn eydem, di mekhutn

00:24:46.906 --> 00:24:50.360
un er hot im tsurikge- er hot im gerufn

00:24:50.360 --> 00:24:52.840
az er zol kumen helfn

00:24:52.840 --> 00:24:56.025
un azoy iz er arayngeganen in di BUSINESS

00:24:56.031 --> 00:25:00.753
un yetst zenen zey dort, ober di kontakt iz zeyer noent

00:25:00.753 --> 00:25:05.222
vayl zi hot khasene gemakht di kinder, un di kinder zenen do in Yerusholaim

00:25:05.245 --> 00:25:08.783
un ⟨tsu⟩ di tekhter fun mayn tokhter

00:25:08.788 --> 00:25:11.440
vos me darf zogn dem emes

00:25:11.440 --> 00:25:13.130
s'ken nisht zayn nenter.

00:25:13.130 --> 00:25:16.280
s'iz azoy vi mayne eygene k- s'iz eyn kop.

00:25:16.280 --> 00:25:18.880
vos ikh zog un vos ikh vel nisht zogn

00:25:18.880 --> 00:25:20.480
me farshteyt mir oyfn vunk.

00:25:20.480 --> 00:25:23.840
yede vort un yede, in frantseyzish, ahin aher

00:25:23.840 --> 00:25:25.790
s'iz nishto keyn problem.

00:25:25.790 --> 00:25:27.969
un fun dem hob ikh a groyse hanoe

00:25:28.060 --> 00:25:31.918
un ikh hob, ikh hob dos geflegt

00:25:31.941 --> 00:25:34.584
un ikh hob getrakht di gantse tsayt

00:25:34.624 --> 00:25:35.411
di

00:25:35.502 --> 00:25:39.630
fun BEETSEM gornisht, vos bin ikh gevezn, a m-

00:25:39.653 --> 00:25:41.404
a meydl fun Pariz

00:25:41.404 --> 00:25:42.346
vos

00:25:42.825 --> 00:25:45.091
kh'hob gornisht REPRESENTirt

00:25:45.091 --> 00:25:49.771
ken men zogn. nisht keyn raykhe, nisht keyn gebildete. gornisht.

00:25:49.997 --> 00:25:53.551
un di eybershter hot mir gemakht aza matone

00:25:54.047 --> 00:25:55.807
vos er hot mir geshikt

00:25:55.807 --> 00:25:58.209
azelekhene kinder koydem kol

00:25:58.620 --> 00:26:00.943
vos di veytog

00:26:01.101 --> 00:26:02.630
iz gevezn

00:26:02.788 --> 00:26:03.777
az

00:26:03.835 --> 00:26:07.780
az ikh hob nisht gekent firn mayne kinder unter di khupe

00:26:07.780 --> 00:26:09.009
mit mayn man.

00:26:09.268 --> 00:26:11.129
un dos iz a zakh

00:26:11.129 --> 00:26:13.751
vos ikh trog mit mir di gantse tsayt.

00:26:13.808 --> 00:26:15.844
vi azoy s'zol nisht zayn

00:26:15.934 --> 00:26:17.244
dos iz

00:26:17.470 --> 00:26:19.050
a zakh vos

00:26:19.343 --> 00:26:21.800
s'makht mir zeyer shver.

00:26:22.093 --> 00:26:24.520
s'iz a shteyn in harts.

00:26:24.520 --> 00:26:28.579
vi vayt ikh hob prubirt tsu makhn dos beste mit alemen

00:26:28.579 --> 00:26:30.460
ober dos iz a fakt.

00:26:30.460 --> 00:26:33.396
me hot nisht keyn shum kinder

00:26:33.396 --> 00:26:35.486
gebrengt unter di khupe.

00:26:35.486 --> 00:26:37.156
a tate mit a mame.

00:26:37.156 --> 00:26:39.196
vos dos iz di greste

00:26:39.196 --> 00:26:40.490
sh- troym

00:26:40.490 --> 00:26:41.831
fun a lebn.

00:26:41.871 --> 00:26:44.092
vos ken men hobn beser fun dos?

00:26:45.583 --> 00:26:51.267
ober dos iz gevezn di METSIUT. di ershte kind hot ge- untergetrogn

00:26:51.267 --> 00:26:56.657
ah fun di mishpokhe KOENIG, hot men genumen, vos leyder iz, s'iz nisht azoy geganen.

00:26:56.657 --> 00:26:58.510
di tsveyte hot mayn sh-

00:26:58.510 --> 00:27:01.540
tokhter gebrengt zayn bruder unter di khupe

00:27:01.540 --> 00:27:02.810
un azoy vayter.

00:27:02.810 --> 00:27:05.360
dernokhn, di zun hot gebrengt

00:27:05.360 --> 00:27:06.530
un di klenere

00:27:06.530 --> 00:27:09.300
di yingere zun hot zi gebrengt unter di khupe

00:27:09.300 --> 00:27:11.850
ober ikh bin nokhgeganen un

00:27:11.880 --> 00:27:14.636
damolst ale mol iz di

00:27:14.929 --> 00:27:20.812
s- afile tsi ikh hob shoyn gegat mayn man un ales, ober di tate, di tate hot gefelt.

00:27:21.274 --> 00:27:24.477
dos iz di, dos iz gevezn di greste zakh.

00:27:24.477 --> 00:27:28.119
ober yetst, oyf tsuriktsukumen oyf di eyniklekh

00:27:28.193 --> 00:27:31.528
vos keyneynehore s'iz do

00:27:31.855 --> 00:27:33.218
fun mayn zun

00:27:33.218 --> 00:27:36.002
s'iz do, yeder eyner iz zeyer

00:27:36.002 --> 00:27:38.652
groys, ober di, di

00:27:38.652 --> 00:27:41.957
yingere vos zenen khasene gegat

00:27:41.997 --> 00:27:44.370
di tsvey tekhter

00:27:44.511 --> 00:27:45.983
zenen do aleyn.

00:27:45.983 --> 00:27:48.493
zey hobn nisht nisht keyn tate, nisht keyn shviger, vayl

00:27:48.493 --> 00:27:51.213
er iz oykhet in Amerike, un azoy vayter.

00:27:51.396 --> 00:27:54.410
iz ikh hob genumen oyf mir

00:27:54.653 --> 00:27:56.689
az ikh gey zey helfn.

00:27:57.471 --> 00:27:59.231
ikh gey zey nemen.

00:27:59.231 --> 00:28:01.177
dos iz mayn flikht.

00:28:01.673 --> 00:28:06.004
un azoy hob ikh es ongehoybn tsu makhn nisht lang

00:28:06.060 --> 00:28:07.269
tsurik.

00:28:07.663 --> 00:28:09.516
yo, iz ⟨hert⟩ zikh

00:28:09.516 --> 00:28:11.090
UNK
